We are excited to announce our Kick-off Workshop: "Think Like An Artist" presented by Bryan Ohno. This interactive, hands-on studio session will inspire and inform you to stimulate and sustain your creativity in both your personal and professional life. It examines the essence of artistic thinking and how to activate your imagination on a consistent basis. 
Come prepared to be unprepared. Participants will take part in stimulating and engaging activities, be encouraged to operate beyond their comfort zone, and given skills to apply innovative solutions in the workplace.
